[2] USA: excess mortality
[There is a correction of this report: COVID-19 update (453): Rapid breath test, excess mortality, masks, WHO, global -- [2] Excess
mortality comment/correction. There was a mistake in the calculation/interpretation of the excess mortality data in the original
